The article is a press release from the White House Office of the Press Secretary, dated June 11, 2010. It discusses a letter sent by Admiral Thad Allen, National Incident Commander, to Carl-Henric Svanberg, President of the Board of Directors of BP. The letter invites Svanberg to a meeting with the President and other senior officials involved in the response to the BP oil spill. The press release provides a link to view the letter.